<h2 id="who-its-for">🎯 Who This Stack Is For</h2>

This luxury retail tech stack configuration serves specific operator profiles:

**Established luxury brands with 3+ locations** ready to professionalize their technology infrastructure. You've outgrown cobbled-together solutions and need integrated platforms that scale.

**High-AOV e-commerce brands expanding into retail** who need omnichannel capabilities from day one. Your online customers expect recognition and continuity when visiting physical locations.

**Premium service retailers** including high-end salons, medical spas, and specialty services where relationship depth drives lifetime value. The clienteling and CRM components translate directly to appointment-based businesses.

**Growing luxury operators** processing $2M+ annually who can justify the platform investments and have the transaction volume to leverage sophisticated tools effectively.

This stack is **not appropriate** for operators still validating product-market fit, brands competing primarily on price, or businesses without the margin structure to support premium technology investments. If your average transaction is below $200, mass-market tools likely serve you adequately.

